.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aBanking lawxHistoryy20th century. 0aBanking lawxHistoryy21st century. 0aBanking law. 0aFinancial crises. 0aGlobal Financial Crisis, 2008-2009. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economic History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311063898140uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030023183040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300231830423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300231830/original  a978-3-11-063898-1  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles